WEBVTT

01:43.280 --> 01:44.160
Sir,

01:44.960 --> 01:45.920
take care.

01:55.320 --> 01:56.320
I'm going.

02:20.600 --> 02:22.200
Why are you in such a hurry?

02:58.000 --> 02:59.120
Wait.

02:59.840 --> 03:02.240
From what I remember, you never left.

03:04.040 --> 03:06.240
Sir, you must be mistaken.

03:07.120 --> 03:08.760
I've been teaching
in Beijing this whole time.

03:11.600 --> 03:12.520
Officer He.

03:14.560 --> 03:15.520
It's really you.

03:17.400 --> 03:18.360
Xiaohe, right?

03:20.720 --> 03:21.680
You don't recognize me?

03:22.960 --> 03:24.960
It's me. Qian Daqun.

03:25.040 --> 03:26.880
I used to be the property manager
at Yuanlongli.

03:26.960 --> 03:28.840
Now I'm just doing alright.

03:28.920 --> 03:32.040
I'm a deputy manager
for the new developer there.

03:32.760 --> 03:35.160
I'm handling Yuanlongli's
relocation project.

03:35.760 --> 03:36.600
What a coincidence.

03:37.600 --> 03:38.640
Ran's back.

03:38.720 --> 03:40.280
He's back too.

03:40.800 --> 03:41.920
Who?

03:42.000 --> 03:43.760
Mr. Qian, you must be busy.

03:43.840 --> 03:45.480
We won't hold you up.

03:45.560 --> 03:46.680
What do you mean by who?

03:46.760 --> 03:48.320
My apprentice, Ran Fangxu.

03:48.400 --> 03:49.480
You don't know him?

03:50.320 --> 03:51.600
Isn't Ran Fangxu already dead?

03:53.160 --> 03:54.400
What are you on about?

03:54.480 --> 03:55.720
Have you lost your mind?

03:55.800 --> 03:57.240
He's standing right here.

03:57.840 --> 03:59.200
What kind of nonsense is that?

03:59.720 --> 04:03.520
I get it. Officer He,
you're messing with me, right?

04:04.120 --> 04:06.040
It's broad daylight.
You're not scaring me.

04:06.120 --> 04:09.280
Still, Officer Ran passed away so young.

04:09.360 --> 04:11.280
It's a real shame.

04:11.360 --> 04:13.800
Are you blind? Ran's right…

04:13.880 --> 04:14.720
WEIYANG STATION

04:17.600 --> 04:18.440
Ran?

04:20.800 --> 04:21.880
Ran Fangxu?

04:21.959 --> 04:23.480
He was here.

04:24.920 --> 04:27.080
What's wrong with him? Has he gone senile?

04:27.160 --> 04:30.000
When Officer Ran died, it was brutal.
Even I know about that.

04:30.080 --> 04:31.120
-Stop talking.
-How could he not know?

04:31.200 --> 04:32.960
What did you say? Shut your trap!

04:33.040 --> 04:33.960
-Dad.
-Officer He.

04:34.040 --> 04:35.520
-What did you just say?
-Stop!

04:35.600 --> 04:37.160
Let's not argue with him. Mr. Qian.

04:37.240 --> 04:38.520
You should go.

04:39.120 --> 04:40.560
-Dad.
-He must be senile.

04:41.400 --> 04:43.160
He Xiaohe, what's wrong with you?

04:43.240 --> 04:45.120
He kept saying Mr. Ran was dead.

04:45.200 --> 04:46.240
Didn't you hear him?

04:46.320 --> 04:47.760
You should've backed me up
and shut him down.

04:47.840 --> 04:48.880
We should beat him up.

04:48.960 --> 04:50.000
Ran Fangxu.

04:51.000 --> 04:53.200
Where are you? Ran Fangxu,

04:53.800 --> 04:55.440
-come out.
-Dad.

04:55.520 --> 04:56.840
I'll say it one more time. Stop hiding.

04:56.920 --> 04:58.040
-Dad, listen to me.
-Let go.

04:58.720 --> 05:01.120
Ran Fangxu! Get out here!

05:01.200 --> 05:02.080
Dad.

05:02.160 --> 05:03.200
Don't stop me.

05:03.280 --> 05:05.640
I'm going to the station right now
to pull the surveillance footage.

05:05.720 --> 05:07.480
I'll find out where he's hiding.

05:07.560 --> 05:09.720
Let go. Ran Fangxu!

05:09.800 --> 05:10.720
Get out here!

05:10.800 --> 05:12.600
-Dad.
-What are you doing?

05:13.200 --> 05:14.360
Let go.

05:14.440 --> 05:15.440
What are you doing?

05:15.960 --> 05:17.240
Ran Fangxu!

05:17.320 --> 05:18.800
Come out, Ran Fangxu!

05:18.880 --> 05:20.360
Where are you hiding, rascal?

05:20.440 --> 05:21.520
Get out here!

05:22.840 --> 05:25.920
-Did you hear me?
-Mr. Ran is already dead.

05:29.960 --> 05:31.320
What… What did you say?

05:37.520 --> 05:38.400
Mr. Ran has been dead.

05:42.760 --> 05:44.360
For twelve years.

05:54.360 --> 05:56.520
Young man, have you seen Ran?

05:56.600 --> 05:58.440
Ran Fangxu's holed up in the archives.

05:59.240 --> 06:01.000
He won't pick up his phone.

06:01.080 --> 06:02.240
Slacker.

06:02.840 --> 06:04.200
This is He.

06:10.120 --> 06:12.040
-Sir.
-What is that?

06:15.160 --> 06:16.520
Don't waste my time.

06:16.600 --> 06:17.720
Get out of the car.

06:18.840 --> 06:20.000
Out now.

06:20.760 --> 06:24.360
Something's wrong with this place.

06:24.440 --> 06:28.880
Let go. I want to know
how I end up on that wall.

06:33.520 --> 06:34.760
Easy, easy.

06:36.400 --> 06:37.560
Ran!

06:39.160 --> 06:40.120
Ran!

06:42.800 --> 06:43.800
Ran!

06:45.760 --> 06:47.520
Hurry up.

06:48.920 --> 06:50.160
You're so clumsy.

07:00.440 --> 07:02.040
Stop playing dumb.

07:03.360 --> 07:04.480
Mr. He,

07:05.520 --> 07:08.200
it's time to let go.

07:09.000 --> 07:09.920
Dad.

07:10.440 --> 07:11.920
Don't dwell on the past.

07:12.000 --> 07:15.880
Once we join hands, we are unstoppable.

07:16.480 --> 07:18.600
Sir, just let it go.

07:18.680 --> 07:21.320
It's not worth spending your whole life
chasing one case.

07:21.920 --> 07:24.840
If you hadn't insisted on digging into it,

07:24.920 --> 07:27.440
who knows how many more lives
this cursed building would've taken?

07:29.520 --> 07:30.440
He.

07:33.400 --> 07:35.440
Just let Ran go.

07:35.520 --> 07:39.560
As your mentor, I'm ordering you
to stay in Weiyang.

08:10.840 --> 08:14.360
Sir, did you bring me here
to look for the kid?

08:14.440 --> 08:15.760
Or for something else?

08:15.840 --> 08:17.600
Why do you keep coming back to Yuanlongli?

08:17.680 --> 08:19.680
I can't keep an eye on him,
restrain him, or stop him.

08:19.760 --> 08:22.120
Sir, stop going to Yuanlongli.

08:22.200 --> 08:24.080
You're not to touch
the Yuanlongli case again.

08:24.160 --> 08:25.440
And you're not to go back there either.

08:25.520 --> 08:28.240
You've brought me here again and again.
What exactly are you trying to do?

08:28.320 --> 08:29.160
Not even once more.

08:29.240 --> 08:31.320
You just want to keep me in Weiyang

08:31.400 --> 08:32.960
and pull me back into the case
from 18 years ago, don't you?

08:33.039 --> 08:34.400
-And then what?
-Then,

08:34.480 --> 08:37.320
he stays in Weiyang and returns
to the Criminal Department.

08:38.120 --> 08:39.799
Sir, stop going to Yuanlongli.

08:39.880 --> 08:41.720
-Just let Ran go.
-Stop dwelling on the past.

08:41.799 --> 08:43.360
It's time to let go.

08:43.440 --> 08:45.360
-Stop going back there.
-Stop dwelling on the past.

08:45.440 --> 08:47.160
Sir, just let it go.

08:47.240 --> 08:48.600
I can't.

08:54.560 --> 08:56.920
Sir, I'm going.

08:57.000 --> 08:58.160
Take care.

08:58.840 --> 09:00.040
Dad!

09:01.640 --> 09:06.840
NO. 1 PEOPLE'S HOSPITAL

09:20.240 --> 09:22.400
CARDIOLOGY

09:26.400 --> 09:27.520
Xiaohe.

09:29.120 --> 09:29.840
Xiaohe.

09:34.520 --> 09:37.880
Why is Mr. He's episode
taking so long this time?

09:37.960 --> 09:39.240
He's even been hospitalized.

09:39.320 --> 09:41.760
He ran into a real case
at Yuanlongli this time.

09:43.000 --> 09:43.840
A real case?

09:47.480 --> 09:51.200
These past two years,
every time he thought he saw Mr. Ran,

09:51.280 --> 09:52.760
he'd drag him back
to Yuanlongli to investigate.

09:53.440 --> 09:54.760
I couldn't stop him.

09:55.280 --> 09:57.200
So I worked with everyone.

09:57.880 --> 10:00.000
We staged a fake missing child case
to keep him occupied.

10:00.720 --> 10:03.240
Ms. Feng, Ma Qiang, and Li Tieling.

10:03.320 --> 10:04.640
They all helped me.

10:04.720 --> 10:06.360
Once the child was found,

10:06.440 --> 10:08.480
we'd take Mr. Ran
to the train station and send him off.

10:08.560 --> 10:10.320
And my dad would snap out of it.

10:13.480 --> 10:15.680
We didn't expect
there to actually be a missing child

10:15.760 --> 10:17.680
in Yuanlongli this time.

10:18.320 --> 10:19.640
Things got out of our hands.

10:20.840 --> 10:24.880
At the station just now, Qian Dajun
insisted on saying Mr. Ran had already…

10:31.120 --> 10:32.160
Qian Dajun, seriously?

10:32.240 --> 10:33.880
Does he think before he speaks?

10:34.720 --> 10:36.440
Wasted everyone's time.

10:38.040 --> 10:39.720
The patient's awake. You can go in now.

10:42.560 --> 10:43.600
Dad,

10:44.280 --> 10:45.520
are you feeling any better?

10:47.080 --> 10:49.640
Mr. He, I'm Qiao.

10:50.280 --> 10:51.720
Are you alright?

10:51.800 --> 10:54.320
Mr. He, I'm Zhao Jie.

10:54.400 --> 10:56.120
The team is here to visit you.

11:07.640 --> 11:09.080
He Yuanhang, are you clear-headed or not?

11:09.160 --> 11:10.000
Answer us.

11:12.120 --> 11:13.160
He,

11:13.920 --> 11:15.960
Captain Ran just called.

11:16.040 --> 11:17.520
He's arrived in Beijing.

11:17.600 --> 11:18.840
He told you not to worry.

11:18.920 --> 11:20.160
Yeah.

11:20.240 --> 11:21.840
Captain Ran heard you were hospitalized.

11:21.920 --> 11:22.960
He was worried sick.

11:23.040 --> 11:24.400
-He asked me to--
-Enough.

11:27.240 --> 11:28.440
I remember everything now.

11:29.720 --> 11:30.600
Ran

11:31.440 --> 11:32.720
is gone.

11:42.320 --> 11:45.600
The whole team has been going
along with this for over two years.

11:45.680 --> 11:49.520
If it flares up again, no one can take it.

11:52.240 --> 11:53.280
Xiaohe.

11:55.640 --> 11:58.640
In the first few years
after Captain Ran passed away,

11:59.440 --> 12:00.360
I used to dream about him all the time.

12:02.080 --> 12:05.960
Everyone on the force
who knew him missed him.

12:07.280 --> 12:08.320
Right.

12:08.400 --> 12:10.960
Every time we hit a tough case, we think,

12:11.480 --> 12:12.800
if only Captain Ran were still here.

12:12.880 --> 12:15.480
But he's passed away for many years.

12:15.560 --> 12:19.560
He wouldn't want us
to sigh over him every day.

12:20.400 --> 12:21.440
It's meaningless.

12:24.640 --> 12:26.640
Go back and talk to Mr. He.

12:27.320 --> 12:28.200
He needs to move on.

12:45.720 --> 12:46.840
Xiaohe.

12:51.000 --> 12:53.360
I know a really good therapist.

12:53.440 --> 12:55.800
Take Mr. He to see him when you have time.

12:55.880 --> 12:58.000
TONG YUNKAI, PSYCHOLOGIST

13:19.720 --> 13:21.200
GET RICH

15:52.120 --> 15:54.280
The Japan-Korea FIFA World Cup
is about to begin.

15:54.360 --> 15:56.200
China, making its first-ever
World Cup appearance,

15:56.280 --> 16:00.360
has been drawn into Group C
with Brazil, Turkey, and Costa Rica.

16:00.440 --> 16:04.120
Let us look forward to a strong showing
from our national team.

16:08.560 --> 16:12.520
WE ADVANCED
2002 KOREA-JAPAN FIFA WORLD CUP

16:16.160 --> 16:20.080
REFORM FOR GROWTH

16:20.160 --> 16:21.520
You're here, Officer He.

16:25.000 --> 16:26.680
Check the tire pressure. Top it up.

16:27.880 --> 16:29.840
You've been driving this junk for years.

16:29.920 --> 16:31.800
You're a deputy station chief now.

16:31.880 --> 16:34.000
Why won't you get a better car? Right?

16:34.080 --> 16:35.440
I don't have money.

16:36.120 --> 16:37.480
My daughter just started middle school.

16:37.560 --> 16:39.000
Everything costs money.

16:40.320 --> 16:41.480
Officer He,

16:41.560 --> 16:43.120
you and your wife have…

16:45.240 --> 16:47.480
Don't even start.

16:47.560 --> 16:48.680
Hurry up. I have to fetch my girl.

16:49.320 --> 16:52.560
‎They pass the ball like this…
‎Team China's special…

16:52.640 --> 16:57.480
Pay up! Pay up! Pay up!

16:57.560 --> 16:59.360
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY, WEIYANG CITY

16:59.440 --> 17:02.400
SAFETY ABOVE ALL

17:02.480 --> 17:04.520
QINGSONG CEMENT FACTORY

17:05.400 --> 17:06.520
What's going on here?

17:07.079 --> 17:08.040
They're demanding unpaid wages.

17:08.560 --> 17:09.720
Nothing new.

17:09.800 --> 17:10.560
PAY UP

17:11.680 --> 17:13.319
Since Wu became the factory director,

17:13.400 --> 17:15.599
business has gone downhill.

17:16.440 --> 17:17.760
It shut down last month.

17:19.280 --> 17:20.760
He owes the workers a year's pay.

17:20.839 --> 17:22.599
-Where's Wu Shanlong?
-He's hiding.

17:23.200 --> 17:25.760
Anywhere there are women,
that's where he'll be.

17:27.040 --> 17:28.200
It's done.

17:28.280 --> 17:31.440
-Pay up!
-Pay up!

17:31.520 --> 17:36.800
SALARY, PAY UP

17:36.880 --> 17:39.880
-Pay up!
-Pay up!

17:39.960 --> 17:42.480
WU SHANLONG

17:49.800 --> 17:53.760
Senior, the problem with this case
is that the scene was washed clean

17:53.840 --> 17:54.840
by last night's heavy rain.

17:54.920 --> 17:56.960
No weapon or usable evidence
has been found.

17:57.040 --> 17:58.240
Officer Liu from Yangguan Branch.

17:58.320 --> 18:00.600
He called Captain Feng
and asked specifically for you to assist.

18:28.800 --> 18:30.360
POLICE

18:31.680 --> 18:33.240
-Hello.
-Hello.

18:33.320 --> 18:34.560
We're with Yangguan Branch.

18:34.640 --> 18:36.800
Hello. Nanshan Branch. Ran Fangxu.

18:36.880 --> 18:38.040
Hello, Captain Ran. Nice to meet you.

18:38.120 --> 18:42.120
MENG FEI FEI

18:42.200 --> 18:46.120
PRICE LIST

18:52.600 --> 18:56.480
Most of the customers of this salon
are passing truck drivers.

18:56.560 --> 18:57.720
Last night, it was raining heavily.

18:57.800 --> 18:59.680
Only the owner and two girls were inside.

19:00.280 --> 19:01.680
That gave the killer the perfect chance.

19:02.480 --> 19:03.720
There were two more victims inside.

19:30.520 --> 19:32.840
It happened around 3 a.m.

19:34.080 --> 19:35.560
Thunderstorm was at its peak.

19:35.640 --> 19:38.040
The killer used a blunt object
to strike the victims' heads

19:38.120 --> 19:39.440
and killed all three women,

19:39.520 --> 19:42.040
then took the cash and jewelry.

19:42.560 --> 19:44.480
The murder weapon is still missing.

19:46.760 --> 19:47.680
Right.

19:47.760 --> 19:50.480
Before leaving, the killer
turned on every faucet

19:50.560 --> 19:51.840
and left all the windows open.

19:51.920 --> 19:54.560
The place was flooded inside and out.
The scene was thoroughly cleaned.

19:55.400 --> 19:57.920
Right now, we can't find anything usable.

20:04.240 --> 20:05.880
Thunderstorm. The fields are muddy.

20:05.960 --> 20:06.880
No one can get through.

20:06.960 --> 20:09.400
There are two cameras
about a kilometer apart along the highway.

20:09.480 --> 20:10.640
We checked the footage.

20:10.720 --> 20:11.760
And guess what.

20:12.520 --> 20:14.560
Because of the storm,
the road conditions were terrible.

20:14.640 --> 20:16.400
In the hour before and after the crime,

20:16.480 --> 20:18.680
not a single car,
not a single person passed.

20:18.760 --> 20:21.280
This is basically an impossible crime.

20:35.160 --> 20:39.000
MENG FEI FEI

20:56.920 --> 20:59.440
Senior, did you find anything?

21:00.160 --> 21:02.440
Zhao Jie, you're older than me.

21:02.520 --> 21:04.000
Don't call me senior.

21:04.520 --> 21:05.520
No way.

21:21.200 --> 21:23.720
What's Captain Ran doing?

21:24.320 --> 21:26.120
Is he here to solve the case
or just take a stroll?

21:27.760 --> 21:29.560
My senior works with creative thinking.

21:30.240 --> 21:32.760
-If you want to learn, talk less.
-Alright.

21:35.640 --> 21:36.640
Oh my.

21:42.760 --> 21:43.760
Senior.

21:45.680 --> 21:46.840
Zhao Jie.

22:13.280 --> 22:15.520
This black raincoat
is missing a plastic button.

22:15.600 --> 22:17.160
It matches the one in the victim's hand.

22:17.680 --> 22:20.160
This was likely discarded by the suspect.

22:20.240 --> 22:21.800
Right. This is it.

22:22.400 --> 22:25.200
Captain Ran, how did you know
there'd be a clue here?

22:25.840 --> 22:27.280
Complacency over distance.

22:27.360 --> 22:29.880
The farther from the scene, the more
the suspect lets their guard down,

22:29.960 --> 22:31.040
the easier they slip up.

22:31.640 --> 22:32.480
It was raining heavily last night.

22:32.560 --> 22:34.120
The killer had no choice
but to escape along the highway.

22:34.200 --> 22:36.560
The farther they got, the safer they felt,

22:37.160 --> 22:39.760
and the more eager they were
to get rid of that bloodstained raincoat.

22:40.440 --> 22:42.920
He thought dumping it this far out
would keep it from being found.

22:43.000 --> 22:45.000
But there are cameras all along the road.

22:45.080 --> 22:46.760
How did none of them catch him?

22:50.040 --> 22:52.360
Because the drainage ditch
is a blind spot.

22:53.440 --> 22:56.600
The suspect likely parked
outside the camera range.

22:57.200 --> 23:00.240
They walked along the ditch
to avoid detection,

23:00.320 --> 23:03.040
then circled back after the crime
and drove off.

23:03.120 --> 23:05.120
That's why the cameras didn't pick him up.

23:05.920 --> 23:09.440
Now all we need to do is check
the cameras at both ends of this road

23:09.520 --> 23:11.720
and look for vehicles that linger
or double back.

23:11.800 --> 23:13.440
That should lead us
straight to the suspect.

23:17.800 --> 23:18.720
Convinced now?

23:23.680 --> 23:30.560
WEIYANG PUBLIC SECURITY BUREAU
NANSHAN BRANCH

23:30.640 --> 23:32.160
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

23:39.960 --> 23:40.920
Captain Feng.

23:41.640 --> 23:44.600
Ran Fangxu, after this,

23:44.680 --> 23:46.760
your reputation as a top detective
will be firmly established.

23:47.960 --> 23:50.240
Yangguan Branch just called.

23:50.320 --> 23:52.680
They've identified the suspect.

23:52.760 --> 23:53.640
How long did that take?

23:53.720 --> 23:55.720
Not even half a day.

23:58.520 --> 23:59.600
Well done.

24:01.040 --> 24:02.960
Everyone, not to brag,

24:03.040 --> 24:05.320
but the first time
I met Captain Ran, I had a feeling

24:05.400 --> 24:07.600
he'd be the rising star in our force.

24:07.680 --> 24:09.400
Don't hype me up.

24:09.480 --> 24:10.920
As long as we catch the criminal,
that's enough.

24:11.000 --> 24:12.560
Those titles are over the top.

24:12.640 --> 24:13.960
Not at all.

24:14.040 --> 24:15.040
Stay grounded.

24:15.120 --> 24:16.400
Keep up the good work.

24:16.480 --> 24:17.520
Don't worry, Captain Feng.

24:21.600 --> 24:22.560
Captain Ran,

24:22.640 --> 24:24.440
you've always kept a low profile.

24:24.520 --> 24:26.120
If it were He Yuanhang,

24:26.200 --> 24:27.760
he'd have taken all the credit
straight to Director Zou.

24:27.840 --> 24:29.840
Right? Here. Have some water.

24:30.680 --> 24:31.800
Qu.

24:33.480 --> 24:36.640
Why has He been avoiding me
all these years?

24:36.720 --> 24:38.000
Any idea why?

24:38.520 --> 24:39.400
What else could it be?

24:39.480 --> 24:40.880
Jealousy, of course.

24:41.520 --> 24:43.720
Back then, you two partnered up
and cracked that missing persons case,

24:43.800 --> 24:45.720
then made a name in the mining case.

24:45.800 --> 24:47.720
When he got back,
he was so full of himself.

24:47.800 --> 24:49.760
His ego was through the roof.

24:50.360 --> 24:51.560
Now look at things.

24:51.640 --> 24:53.400
You've been promoted to deputy captain,

24:53.480 --> 24:55.240
and he's still stuck where he is.

24:56.360 --> 24:58.200
I heard he and his wife…

25:00.160 --> 25:01.960
Fine. Forget it. Let's drop it.

25:18.280 --> 25:19.720
THIEVES WILL BE PUNISHED

25:19.800 --> 25:22.080
Cluck, cluck, cluck.

25:26.080 --> 25:27.560
Red Crown.

25:32.080 --> 25:34.160
Where did General White go?

25:40.080 --> 25:41.560
General White?

25:44.240 --> 25:45.640
General White.

25:52.400 --> 25:53.440
General White.

25:54.720 --> 25:56.160
General White.

26:03.760 --> 26:05.240
General White.

26:17.320 --> 26:19.080
Someone died!

26:19.160 --> 26:21.720
Someone died!

27:39.880 --> 27:41.800
This old man's teeth
are quite distinctive.

27:58.880 --> 28:00.480
Hey, heard about that smuggling case?

28:00.560 --> 28:03.200
-No luck. Haven't found it yet.
-Not yet?

28:03.280 --> 28:04.920
-Officer He.
-Officer He, you're back.

28:05.000 --> 28:06.360
Officer He, is that heavy?

28:06.440 --> 28:07.920
Want me to carry that to my desk?

28:08.000 --> 28:08.880
What are you on about?

28:08.960 --> 28:10.240
You think they are all yours?

28:10.320 --> 28:14.040
Same as always. Everyone has a share.

28:14.640 --> 28:16.200
Look at you two.

28:16.280 --> 28:18.160
The training site
was in the middle of nowhere.

28:18.240 --> 28:19.160
Nothing to buy.

28:19.240 --> 28:21.120
I just grabbed
some dried fish and shrimp paste.

28:21.760 --> 28:23.880
-Where's Shouhu? Shouhu.
-Yes.

28:23.960 --> 28:24.920
Come on. Quick.

28:25.000 --> 28:26.080
Give these to everyone.

28:26.600 --> 28:27.960
Officer He is back from training.

28:28.040 --> 28:29.640
-Officer He is back.
-Officer He.

28:29.720 --> 28:30.680
-Officer He.
-Officer He.

28:30.760 --> 28:32.240
-Officer He.
-You're so thoughtful.

28:32.320 --> 28:33.720
-Quite a lot!
-We have sent him

28:33.800 --> 28:35.400
-whenever there is a training.
-It's mine.

28:35.480 --> 28:36.800
-Officer He. You're back.
-Officer He said we share these.

28:36.880 --> 28:38.080
-Yeah.
-Officer He said we share these.

28:38.160 --> 28:39.600
-He didn't ask you to pick what you like.
-How was everything going?

28:39.680 --> 28:41.480
Nothing unusual happened

28:41.560 --> 28:43.200
while I was away, right?

28:43.280 --> 28:44.640
All good. Nothing unusual.

28:44.720 --> 28:47.000
-Good.
-Nothing unusual?

28:47.080 --> 28:48.200
They found a skull in Yuanlongli.

28:49.560 --> 28:50.720
Yuanlongli?

28:51.720 --> 28:52.800
A skull?

28:52.880 --> 28:53.840
Is that a murder case?

28:53.920 --> 28:55.120
Here's the situation, Officer He.

28:55.200 --> 28:58.640
Yesterday morning, a skull was found
on the rooftop of New York Block.

28:58.720 --> 29:02.080
But the branch has taken over.
It's out of our hands.

29:04.600 --> 29:05.760
What about Ran Fangxu?
Did he go check it out?

29:06.360 --> 29:07.200
He did.

29:07.280 --> 29:10.040
I think it's quite serious.

29:14.400 --> 29:15.120
RAN

29:29.760 --> 29:33.320
FAIR AND JUST, LOYAL AND TRUE

29:40.040 --> 29:42.080
Officer He, what brings you here?

29:42.160 --> 29:43.480
What's this?

29:43.560 --> 29:45.120
Was it found in Yuanlongli?

29:45.200 --> 29:47.080
It's related to the June 30th case
you worked on.

29:47.160 --> 29:48.760
It's related? How?

29:52.560 --> 29:53.760
We recovered hair samples
from the victim's home.

29:53.840 --> 29:56.720
DNA comparison confirms
the skull belongs to Xu Zhihong.

29:59.520 --> 30:00.440
Homicide?

30:01.040 --> 30:04.120
A single skull isn't enough
to determine the cause of death.

30:04.200 --> 30:05.600
But look at this.

30:06.120 --> 30:08.720
There's a fracture
at the back of the skull.

30:08.800 --> 30:11.160
Uneven edges. Dark red coloration.

30:14.800 --> 30:15.880
That suggests a blunt impact

30:15.960 --> 30:17.080
to the back of the head
while the victim was alive.

30:17.160 --> 30:18.520
And with bleeding.

30:20.200 --> 30:21.680
Here.

30:21.760 --> 30:24.600
A linear cut
on the lower right rear of the skull.

30:24.680 --> 30:25.760
Deep to the bone.

30:26.400 --> 30:28.600
Clean edges. No vital reaction.

30:28.680 --> 30:31.320
That cut was made after death,
likely during dismemberment.

30:32.280 --> 30:33.880
High probability of homicide.

30:36.520 --> 30:37.440
Time of death?

30:38.040 --> 30:40.440
About five years ago. 1997.

30:55.480 --> 30:56.600
Where's he?

30:57.200 --> 30:58.840
He's not answering his phone.

31:01.640 --> 31:03.840
Alright. Got it.

31:07.400 --> 31:08.240
Captain Feng.

31:10.720 --> 31:14.320
REFLECTION REPORT ON YUANLONGLI
JUNE 30TH CASE. HE YUANHANG

31:16.440 --> 31:17.640
What's this?

31:21.440 --> 31:22.600
Captain Feng,

31:23.280 --> 31:24.600
the Yuanlongli case

31:24.680 --> 31:26.080
has now gone
from missing persons to homicide.

31:27.760 --> 31:30.200
Ran and I made a mistake.

31:30.720 --> 31:32.240
But I need to make one thing clear.

31:32.840 --> 31:35.400
Back then, I was leading
the investigation.

31:35.480 --> 31:38.200
-This has nothing to do with Ran.
-He Yuanhang.

31:39.080 --> 31:40.680
That's not how you cover
for your apprentice.

31:41.360 --> 31:42.720
In the case summary,

31:42.800 --> 31:45.280
Ran Fangxu's name was listed before yours.

31:45.360 --> 31:48.640
That alone puts
primary responsibility on him.

31:49.320 --> 31:50.760
I was being humble.

31:50.840 --> 31:52.400
I put his name first on purpose.

31:53.000 --> 31:55.840
He was a fresh graduate. What did he know?

31:55.920 --> 31:57.120
He knew nothing.

31:57.200 --> 32:00.560
Captain Feng,
I request disciplinary action.

32:01.400 --> 32:03.160
Is this about discipline?

32:03.840 --> 32:05.720
You think this isn't embarrassing enough?

32:09.040 --> 32:10.120
PERSONNEL TRANSFER APPLICATION FORM

32:12.920 --> 32:13.960
What is this again?

32:14.040 --> 32:17.000
Can you second me here again?

32:17.080 --> 32:19.080
Assign me full-time to this case.

32:19.160 --> 32:21.400
I guarantee, in…

32:21.920 --> 32:23.280
in one week,

32:23.360 --> 32:24.440
I'll crack it.

32:24.520 --> 32:27.920
-Then…
-Then you mess it up again?

32:28.520 --> 32:29.360
No, I…

32:29.440 --> 32:32.880
Captain Feng, I want to get rid
of this stupid brat for good.

32:32.960 --> 32:34.480
He Yuanhang.

32:35.320 --> 32:37.280
You're late for that.

32:37.360 --> 32:42.360
Since the skull was found,
that brat hasn't left Yuanlongli.

32:42.440 --> 32:44.840
He's not even answering my calls.

32:52.680 --> 32:56.320
A smooth road
never makes a great detective.

32:57.520 --> 33:02.120
Let's consider this case a test for him.

33:04.440 --> 33:05.360
Point taken.

33:06.920 --> 33:10.400
That's why you're the boss.

33:13.280 --> 33:14.200
And this…

33:14.280 --> 33:16.200
PERSONNEL TRANSFER APPLICATION FORM

33:17.880 --> 33:19.440
I'm not signing that.

33:20.320 --> 33:23.160
Even if I bring you here,
you'll just try to leave again

33:23.240 --> 33:25.280
-in a few days.
-No, not at this time.

33:25.360 --> 33:26.800
If I don't crack this case,

33:26.880 --> 33:28.120
I won't leave even
if you beat me to death.

33:29.320 --> 33:30.400
I mean it.

33:32.640 --> 33:35.200
The submission process is all wrong.

33:35.280 --> 33:36.520
Leave the form here. I'll handle it.

33:37.760 --> 33:41.160
This time, we'll push him again.

33:41.240 --> 33:43.720
He has to get back up where he fell.

33:44.560 --> 33:45.520
One day,

33:45.600 --> 33:50.000
when he takes this seat, he'll win
everyone's hearts and minds.

33:50.680 --> 33:52.000
I'll make sure of it.

33:56.840 --> 34:02.360
YUANLONGLI INTERNATIONAL GARDEN

34:15.360 --> 34:17.360
How am I supposed to interfere
with a police investigation?

34:17.440 --> 34:18.960
-But you should do something!
-Yes!

34:19.040 --> 34:22.520
Officer He, could you go talk
to Officer Ran?

34:23.199 --> 34:26.080
-What's going on with Ran Fangxu?
-He's lost it.

34:26.159 --> 34:27.800
Since yesterday,

34:27.880 --> 34:29.840
he's dug up everything
from downstairs to the rooftop.

34:30.520 --> 34:32.719
Even the parking garage
and outside the compound.

34:34.280 --> 34:35.480
Where is he? Where is he now?

34:36.320 --> 34:37.480
Still on the roof, I think.

35:01.280 --> 35:02.280
Ran Fangxu!

35:04.320 --> 35:05.640
Ran Fangxu.

35:09.520 --> 35:11.360
Ran Fangxu. Stop.

35:12.440 --> 35:14.280
I said stop. Did you hear me?

35:16.000 --> 35:17.280
This isn't investigating.

35:17.360 --> 35:19.040
This is vandalism.

35:21.000 --> 35:23.600
Stop. Stop it. Did you hear me?

35:24.880 --> 35:26.760
What's wrong with you?

35:34.600 --> 35:36.000
It's approved.

35:36.600 --> 35:38.680
We're partnering up again.

35:38.760 --> 35:41.680
We cracked this case five years ago.

35:41.760 --> 35:44.040
We can crack it again now.

35:46.320 --> 35:48.640
But Xu Meng and her dad
aren't coming back.

35:52.320 --> 35:53.360
Five years ago,

35:54.560 --> 35:56.200
they went through so much

35:56.840 --> 35:58.680
to make themselves disappear

35:59.200 --> 36:01.120
just to stay alive.

36:01.800 --> 36:02.880
And in the end…

36:08.080 --> 36:10.720
If I hadn't rushed to a conclusion,

36:12.800 --> 36:14.160
if I'd kept digging,

36:16.720 --> 36:18.400
maybe they wouldn't have died.

36:21.720 --> 36:23.680
Stop thinking that way, please.

36:23.760 --> 36:26.120
You can't solve cases based on "ifs".

36:26.200 --> 36:28.600
Right now, we need to find the killer.

36:28.680 --> 36:30.800
Even if we do,

36:32.720 --> 36:34.360
it won't bring them back.

36:35.920 --> 36:38.560
Ran Fangxu, snap out of it already.

36:38.640 --> 36:40.960
Now, we've found Xu Zhihong is dead.

36:41.040 --> 36:42.960
We don't know
whether Xu Meng is dead or alive.

36:43.040 --> 36:45.560
We must look into the case again.
She might still be alive.

36:47.560 --> 36:48.520
No, she's not.

36:49.160 --> 36:50.120
No.

36:51.680 --> 36:53.560
I've studied enough missing persons cases.

36:55.200 --> 36:56.840
Xu Meng wouldn't have survived.

37:00.240 --> 37:02.880
My parents went missing together.

37:07.000 --> 37:08.520
When I was in the academy,

37:08.600 --> 37:12.320
I swore I would solve
every missing persons case I took.

37:12.400 --> 37:13.440
But…

37:14.320 --> 37:15.880
Now… My first case…

37:38.120 --> 37:39.840
I failed Xu Meng and her dad.

37:42.960 --> 37:44.600
I failed my parents too.

37:52.720 --> 37:53.640
Ran.

37:53.720 --> 37:55.000
Did you kill them?

37:56.240 --> 37:59.800
No, you didn't. Then stop wasting time
and stop crying over spilled milk.

37:59.880 --> 38:02.200
Let's move and bring
the killer to justice.

38:02.280 --> 38:03.600
That's how you honor them

38:03.680 --> 38:05.560
and your own oath.

38:06.880 --> 38:08.960
Xu Zhihong's been dead for five years.

38:11.000 --> 38:14.920
We had no leads back then.
How do we investigate now?

38:15.000 --> 38:16.640
How do we catch the killer?

38:17.160 --> 38:18.080
This case

38:19.320 --> 38:20.520
is unsolvable.

38:21.200 --> 38:22.640
What did you just say?

38:23.400 --> 38:26.240
I've never once asked
the captain for favors.

38:26.320 --> 38:28.280
This time, I fought to get assigned here,

38:28.880 --> 38:31.520
and you're hiding out,
telling me you can't solve it?

38:34.360 --> 38:35.200
My fault.

38:40.320 --> 38:41.320
It's all my fault.

38:42.920 --> 38:44.600
I don't deserve to be a detective.

38:45.280 --> 38:46.640
Then what?

38:50.040 --> 38:51.000
I'm going back to Beijing

38:52.400 --> 38:53.880
to be a lecturer.

38:53.960 --> 38:54.960
Cut the nonsense.

38:55.040 --> 38:56.240
Let's go. We're working the case now.

38:56.320 --> 38:57.840
Come on. Are you coming or not?

38:59.520 --> 39:01.040
Are you coming or not?
Are you coming or not?

39:05.880 --> 39:07.120
Not coming?

39:07.640 --> 39:08.480
Fine.

39:09.560 --> 39:10.400
If you won't do it,

39:12.880 --> 39:14.840
I will.

39:18.360 --> 39:19.920
You are a coward.

39:28.360 --> 39:29.600
I'll crack it on my own.

39:36.920 --> 39:37.840
He?

39:43.280 --> 39:44.280
He.

39:48.120 --> 39:49.280
He.

39:52.680 --> 39:53.520
He!

39:53.600 --> 39:54.880
He!

40:02.400 --> 40:03.520
He!

40:04.160 --> 40:05.200
He!

40:08.560 --> 40:09.800
He!
